translation: WARNING: This challenge is very difficult, but if you complete the map you will earn immortality on the leaderboard. Your characters will revive when your Daily Objectives reset every day so you can continue your journey.\n\nEarn 800 Orange Gear Materials and 6 full pieces of Orange Gear from the list of possible rewards below when you complete "Enter the Darkness" for the first time. Earn even more rewards when you complete your first timed run. Collect Gold when you complete each node during the first two runs of this challenge.

WARNING: This challenge is insanely difficult, making "Enter the Darkness" look like a walk in the park. Those who complete this challenge will not only gain immortality on the leaderboard but also unlock a unique player avatar frame! Your characters will revive when your Daily Objectives reset every day so you can continue your journey.\n\nEarn 2,400 Orange Gear Materials and 18 full pieces of Orange Gear from the list of possible rewards below when you complete "Fear the Darkness" for the first time, as well as the ultra-powerful Ultron! Earn even more rewards when you complete your first timed run. Collect Gold when you complete each node during the first two runs of this challenge.
Complete {title} once to unlock Timed runs!
Complete the sixteen trials of Fear the Darkness before you can challenge Dormammu's ultimate agent of destruction.
Defeat Dormammu's ultimate agent of destruction, the notorious Ultron, to escape from the Dark Dimension.
Complete the ten trials of Enter the Darkness before you can challenge Dormammu's agent of shadows.
Defeat Dormammu's agent of shadows, the notorious Ultron, to survive the Dark Dimension.
